        { "@type": "Question", "name": "How much does review management software cost?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "From $39/month (BrightLocal) to $1,000+/month (Reputation.com). Most small businesses spend $75 to $299/month. For a single location, $49 to $99 is the right zone. theStacc bundles reviews plus GBP plus content from $49/month." }},
        { "@type": "Question", "name": "Do online reviews affect local SEO rankings?", "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. Google confirms review quantity, quality, and response rate influence Local Pack rankings. Top-3 local results average 47 reviews. A one-star rating increase can boost revenue 5 to 9 percent." }},
