        </div>

        <div class="inline-cta">
          <div class="cta-copy">
            <h4>Skip the standalone review tool — bundle it.</h4>
            <p>theStacc collects reviews, auto-responds across Google/Facebook/Yelp, and posts to your Google Business Profile every week. Reviews <strong>plus</strong> content SEO <strong>plus</strong> GBP — one subscription from $49/mo.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="cta-action">
            <a href="/demo/" class="cta-btn-inline">See a live demo <span>→</span></a>
            <span class="cta-meta">No card · 15-min walkthrough</span>
