          <li><strong>Test accounts</strong> — 4 live local businesses (HVAC, dental, salon, e-commerce), 1–4 locations each.</li>
          <li><strong>Scope</strong> — 90 days of standard service, no custom integrations.</li>
          <li><strong>Measurement</strong> — review velocity, star average lift, response time, GBP impressions (GMB API).</li>
          <li><strong>Total spend</strong> — $4,180 across 10 platforms, Mar–May 2026.</li>
        </ul>

